premise_source_doc_sentence: Lem Dobbs  (  born Anton Lemuel Kitaj ; 24 December 1959  )  is a British-American screenwriter , best known for the films Dark City  (  1998  )  and The Limey  (  1999  )  .
He was born in Oxford , England , and is the son of the painter , R.B. Kitaj .
The nom de plume `` Dobbs '' was taken from the character played by Humphrey Bogart in The Treasure of the Sierra Madre  (  1948  )  .
